<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li><strong>December 16, 2017</strong> - In the newest episode of his podcast <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/theresacactusinthecorner">The Foundation</a>, listen to moderator <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;">Doctor Cimmerian</a></span> do a deep dive on the articles and lore behind the Fifthist Church!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>September 30, 2017</strong> - Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;">DrBleep</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;">Zhange</a></span>, the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/news-08-2017">August Site News</a> page is live! As a note, all site authors with new pages each month can feel free to send a PM to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span> with their own article blurb for the next news page!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>September 18, 2017</strong> - A new fancy module in the sidebar allows for <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-3646159/sidebar-translation-module">translated works</a></strong> to be linked from the original article. Credit to the SCP-RU team for making it possible!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>August 30, 2017</strong> - The <strong><a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com">Wanderers' Library</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://visual-records.wikidot.com">Visual Records</a></strong> Sites have both received significant overhauls! The Library has been tweaking its content presentation for a few months now and has been given a fresh coat of paint! The Visual Records wiki has been scrubbed of all images which were not compliant with the CC-by-SA 3.0 License and can now fulfill its potential as a SCP Fuel and Artwork repository! It has also received a fresh coat of paint! Check 'em out!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>August 25, 2017</strong> - The <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/news-07-2017">July Site News</a> is now posted! Come check out all the new SCP articles, tales, author pages, hub pages, and more that were posted that month, compiled by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>August 14, 2017</strong> - To increase voting and readership for under-reviewed articles, a new site project has been started: the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/young-and-under-30">&quot;Young and under 30&quot;</a> project is aiming to get more attention to articles less than a year old, and with a score of less than +30. Come check it out and participate!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>August 1, 2017</strong> - Fire up the sketchbook and break out your art medium, for the <strong><a href="/social-media-art-contest">Internet Outreach Art Contest</a></strong> is underway! Entries are to be posted throughout the month!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>July 29, 2017</strong> - The <a href="/2017-survey-results">2017 Community Survey results</a> are out! Come see the snapshot of the worldwide SCP community that <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5888483); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5888483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5888483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5888483); return false;">Cyantreuse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;">LurkD</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span> have developed!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>July 17, 2017</strong> - Artkast is live! Join us for this special episode of The Kaktuskast in which <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span> is joined by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/perelka-l" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1940138); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1940138&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Perelka_L" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1940138)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/perelka-l" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1940138); return false;">Perelka_L</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;">Zhange</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span> to talk about art, inspiration, and the sex appeal of the highest levels of senior staff. Check it out at <a href="https://www.djkakt.us/kaktuskast/2017/7/17/the-kaktuskast-ep-24-artkast2017">djkakt.us</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>July 13, 2017</strong> - The Kaktuskast is back! Joining us on this special ReintroductionKast is <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span>, to talk about music, audio, and TroyL's blood! Check the show out at <a href="https://www.djkakt.us/kaktuskast/2017/7/10/the-kaktuskast-ep-23-reintroductionkast">djkakt.us</a>, and check out the first episode of <a href="https://www.djkakt.us/the-foundation/">The Foundation</a>, hosted by staff's own <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;">Doctor Cimmerian</a></span>!</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>July 10, 2017</strong> - Come read the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/news-06-2017">June Site News</a>! Big thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609380041" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span> for compiling all of the new SCP articles, tales, author pages, hub pages, and more that were posted in June!</li>
