<li><strong>December 05, 2010</strong> &#8212; We've got a donation button on the side of the site, in order to help us fund our own ads! Check the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-289630/donation-drive">forums</a> for more information.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>January 12, 2010</strong> &#8212; Front Page has been revised: thanks to Mackenzie for fixing several broken bits.</li>
</ul>
