<li><strong>October 29, 2009</strong> &#8212; New questions up on the application. If you have been given the option of reapplying, now would be the time.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>October 28, 2009</strong> &#8212; Mass Edit is Still In progress. Before applying to the site, please read the <a href="/guide-for-newbies">Guide for Newbies</a>.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>September 09, 2009</strong> &#8212; MASS EDIT IS HERE! Several members of the Senior Staff are going to be going through the entire list, and culling out the weak ones. During this time period, we have frozen the ability to create new pages. Everything else is still doable.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>July 24, 2009</strong> &#8212; There is a new application process. Please complete all of the steps if you wish to join.</li>
